iStallman at the helm will that effort fail?		gopher.black	70
i		gopher.black	70
iHere first I will make an ethical statement that libre software is		gopher.black	70
inot important when juxtaposed by the physical safety of a human		gopher.black	70
ibeing. It is not important when juxtaposed with the safety of		gopher.black	70
iminors, of women, or in relation to sexual abuse. If Richard		gopher.black	70
iStallman was the one and only human being who could make libre		gopher.black	70
