iMozilla and the Tor Project. We must censor Stallman and the FSF		gopher.black	70
iboard of directors. The means of doing so is their removal from		gopher.black	70
ithat position. Let it be done and done peacefully. Let them learn		gopher.black	70
ifrom it as Stallman learned that his 2006 statements were		gopher.black	70
idangerous and damaging. Maybe by removing them from power others		gopher.black	70
iwill learn as well. These ideas they're arguing are widening an		gopher.black	70
iOverton window around sexual consent that doesn't need widening.		gopher.black	70
iLets quiet the extremists and bring that window to a healthier		gopher.black	70
